Author: Fu.Sin
Title: 🚀[ANN][ICO]💖 MBYS - PROFESSIONAL DATA MARKETPLACE💫
Body: You have it written. The mission of MBYS is to create a world of seamless professional recruiting through the dissemination of truthful data. Question. And how will the information provided by the applicant be checked?

Author: MBYSMESH
Title: 🚀[ANN][ICO]💖 MBYS - PROFESSIONAL DATA MARKETPLACE💫
Body: 5 members of your personal network are selected to verify your credentials, and they stake their MESH tokens when they validate your profile to ensure the accuracy of their assessment and prevent abuse.  In order to connect with people on the platform, you have to receive a MESH address from them or physically scan their QR code -- to ensure that the data sold to companies is truthful and usable, you can only sell data once your profile has been verified by 5 users.  Read our whitepaper and join our telegram! https://t.me/mbys_official
